ActOld Age Security Act
SubjectAgreement and Implementing Agreement on Social Security between Canada and Bulgaria Come into Force
PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue giving notice that the AGREEMENT ON SOCIAL SECURITY and the IMPLEMENTING AGREEMENT CONCERNING THE AGREEMENT between Canada and the REPUBLIC OF BULGARIA come into force on March 1, 2014.
